data.text:
Cover Sheets

Cover Sheets are required for all Deed and Land Record documents to be recorded in the Portsmouth Circuit Court Clerk's Office.

Click here to access the .

e-Recording

We are NOW accepting e-Recordings for real estate document which is an efficient, fast, and secure way to get your documents processed and recorded. To get signed up is quick & easy, and you can start e-Recording right away. You may utilize either of the vendors below.

- Click here to visit CSC Global's website

- Click here to visit Simplifile's website

NOTE: A Virginia Land Record Coversheet will still be required for all e-Recordings.

Effective February 1, 2018, there will be an additional $5.00 fee for paper real estate recordings.
